sequenceDiagram
    participant CL as 🟣 Claude Code
    participant OB as 🧠 OpenBrain
    participant CU as 🟢 Cursor
    participant CP as 🟦 Copilot

    Note over CL: Session 1: Plan Hardening
    CL->>CL: Harden execution contract
    CL->>OB: Write: architectural decisions
    CL->>OB: Write: pattern choices
    
    Note over CU: Session 2: Execution
    CU->>OB: Read: all prior decisions
    OB->>CU: Return: Claude's decisions + context
    CU->>CU: Execute slices with full context
    CU->>OB: Write: implementation decisions
    
    Note over CP: Session 3: Review
    CP->>OB: Read: full decision history
    OB->>CP: Return: Claude + Cursor decisions
    CP->>CP: Independent audit
    CP->>OB: Write: review findings
